Description:
    CircSeqAlignTk is a toolkit for the analysis of RNA-Seq data
    derived from circular genome sequences, with a primary focus on viroids,
    circular RNAs typically consisting of a few hundred nucleotides.
    The toolkit supports an end-to-end analysis pipeline,
    from alignment to visualization.
